 Phase 5: Data Engineering & Analytics Architecture

 5.1 Batch Processing
- Concept: Process large volumes of data at scheduled intervals (e.g., nightly job).
- Tool: Apache Spark, Hadoop MapReduce.
- Use case: Monthly billing report, data warehouse ETL.

 5.2 Stream Processing (Real-time)
- Concept: Process data as it arrives, within milliseconds.
- Tool: Apache Flink, Kafka Streams, Spark Streaming.
- Use case: Fraud detection, real-time dashboard, stock ticker.

 5.3 Lambda Architecture (Hybrid)
- Combines Batch (accurate, but slow) + Stream (fast, but approximate) + Serving Layer (to query merged results).
- Complex but powerful: Used by Twitter, Netflix.

